{"tid":263462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（老同）69歲伯伯直播打飛機，","createTime":"2017-05-30T04:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T05:17:14.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dced52a024d851ec75f817dc931a32ecec2b835f","tid":263462,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"美國69歲伯伯上同志網直播自慰　疑刺激過度暴斃<br />\n美國一名69歲伯伯為求刺激上同志網站直播自慰，突然心臟病發倒在椅子上，妻子發現後立刻通知警方，但卻錯過急救時間，由刺激的自慰直播變成急救直播，嚇壞網民。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Information Nigeria》報道，住在美國賓夕法尼亞州的比爾(Bill)今年已經69歲，仍時常在各同志交友網站上游走，日前在一個成人網站直播自慰，疑似因為太興奮，直播到一半突然在椅子上暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n比爾的妻子察覺異狀後，立刻打電話求救，並進行心肺復甦術，醫護人員到場後立刻為比爾進行急救，但可惜已錯過黃金救援時間，比爾不幸身亡。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/915303/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F915303%2F&d=12Vx5pi6AJGYOkyXFKF4jDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=8732eb5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F915303%2F&h=49044905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/915303/</a>"},{"pid":"7a2ae917f6a8e860129940180d59f6e6cb86a0c8","tid":263462,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"刺激的自慰直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}